Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:03.64,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:07.24,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan's logic can heal the dried hearts of modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:09.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The stage this time is a resort hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:10.88,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This case is a huge three-parter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:12.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:16.89,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.98,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Izu Princess Hotel - Private Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:55.17,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shiro Kon'no (28)\NBank Employee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:09.51,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tokio Ebara (32)\NComputer Programmer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:16.94,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Gen'ichiro Kaneshiro (74)\NComputer Company Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.86,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shizue Hayashi (56)\NKaneshiro's Butler
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.47,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hideko Kamijo (29)\NSoftware Company CEO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.73,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Satoru Maeda (30)\NJonan University Electrical Engineering Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:57.22,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Akiko Sayama (24)\NHigh School Math Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.87,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Agasa Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:11.94,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Observation Lounge
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:10.00,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Princess Hotel 2F Pub Emerald
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:45.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I hate this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why am I in such a hot place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:51.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}at such a hot time of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:57.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is all because of\Nthe doc's phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eh? Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:02.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes! Three days and two\Nnights at a hotel in Izu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And for free, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:07.44,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.59,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Free sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:13.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What am I doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:19.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I should be out looking for\Nthose men in black who shrunk me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:28.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But the occasional break is nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NYou should come swim, too, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eh, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only half has been paid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:47.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. A reservation for three in the name of Agasa, right? There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible! Check again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, you! Only half of\Nthe hotel's cost has been paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with paying half then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't bring that\Nmuch money with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:06.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, the doc {\i1}did{\i0} say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:08.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is it {\i1}really{\i0} free?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:11.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In your case, Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}, it's as good as free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In my case? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:14.36,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:19.95,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My scientist friends and I like\Nto communicate via PC lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:24.78,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One of them found an interesting\Ntour on an online forum
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:28.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and invited me to apply for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:31.25,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's called the "Izu Mystery Tour".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.88,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mystery tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:38.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Luckily, my friend, his granddaughter,\Nand I all were chosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:43.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But his granddaughter caught a cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so now I'm offering you our spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:50.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Six parties will attend—\Nten people in all, including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Everyone gets a 50% hotel discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:56.07,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But the tour organizer is one\Nof the other seven people,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:59.45,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and whoever figures out who\Nthat is gets to stay for free
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:04.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and wins floppy disks\Ncontaining a certain program.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:07.66,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Though you wouldn't have a use for the program...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:11.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So how do I look for this\Nmysterious organizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:16.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We received the names and room\Nnumbers of all the attendees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the organizer's supposed\Nto play a certain character
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:23.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and cause an incident during the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.68,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A certain character?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:29.98,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes, a character you know\Nvery well from novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.27,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...the Night Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,3.04 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how long you took\Nto respond to my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was most informative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Shiro Kon'no, Room 2002.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:05:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll never find the Baron's identity that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who\Nanswered in 2.86 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ebara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Room 2101.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you ever shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exposing oneself when caught off-guard
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is{\i0} the way of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Shizue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaneshiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Room 2001...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It took you 6.29 seconds to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My eyes are bad, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never expected you\Nwould question me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all right. I'll know the\Ntruth once I process this data.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that data's incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're still missing\Nsomeone's information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Mr. Night Baron?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What was that,\NKamijo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} of Room 2102?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,0.97 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:06:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Add it in after my\N1.48 seconds, Kon'no{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this Baron thingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean you don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.\NHe's just playin' innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, he shows up in lots of\NShin'ichi's dad's novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:23.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Night Baron is an elusive\Nvillain created by my father, Yusaku Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:31.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's a thief of the darkness\Nand sometimes a crazed murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:36.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My father, Yusaku, hasn't revealed\Nthe Night Baron's identity yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:43.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but either way, whoever's using his\Nname is one these people...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This makes no sense.\NI'm going to our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! What about the money for the hotel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:57.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on. There were\Nsupposed to be ten people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:07:01.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}With me, Ran, the old man and the other five, we're just eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're missing two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's just your butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don'tcha come with me and fill my drinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you Satoru Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}. Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Know? He was Japan's karate champ six years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the reason I started\Npracticing karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Ran Mouri! I won\Nthe recent city championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A karate champ and a city champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never expected to meet\Nyou here! I'm super-lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who's super-lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my fiancée, Akiko Sayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're getting married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't take it personally.\NAkiko gets jealous pretty easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the Night Baron, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Room 1901, Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}... 0.75 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:18.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's still at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's strange. You're supposed to be\Ntwo doctors and a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They couldn't come,\Nso we came in their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was my father, and he's\Na detective, not a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. His name is Kogoro Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen him in the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they say he's a great detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dirty of him to send\Na detective instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come now. We have\Nfewer possible Barons now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:09:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with Kogoro Mouri here,\Nwe cannot afford to show our faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like Dad's famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:07.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All thanks to me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}that's{\i0} the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why they were shocked\Nwhen I said Dad was a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's basically like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I find which of those\Nseven is the Night Baron,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we get to enjoy\Nthe Izu Beach for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's why Dr. Agasa told Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} it was free!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But of course! Because there's no mystery that I, Kogoro Mouri, can't solve!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:57.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You were just ranting about going\Nhome 'cause you have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, then! I better go do\Nmy preliminary questioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's in such high spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you say we look around the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?\NLet's move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay here\Na little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Well, I'll be in the\Ngift shop downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll be there in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:24.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:28.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why were they all so shocked\Nat the mention of a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's just a game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:34.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All you get is to stay\Nfor free, so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:37.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And that murderous glare!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:40.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then there's what\Nthe doc said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:44.97,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...and wins floppy disks\Ncontaining a certain program.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:48.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Though you wouldn't have a use for the program...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've got a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:11:02.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Guess I can just call him after\Ndinner and get all the details...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:03.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He must've changed in the toilet\Nand then taken the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:05.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But who dressed up as\Nthe Night Baron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:10.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Without counting me, Ran or the old man, there's seven people on this tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:17.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The purpose of the tour is to find\Nits organizer among the attendees.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:23.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The organizer who would cause\Nan incident as the Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:27.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But it's just a simple\Ngame to stay for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:32.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who'd push someone off\Njust for {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that program?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.34,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What exactly is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea. All the ad said was that\Nit was the "ultimate program".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me.\NMy doctor friend mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,something or other about a virus...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A virus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's odd, though. He shouldn't\Nknow any more about it than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, doc! Don't tell me that virus is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?! I've been waiting\Nat the gift shop this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?! You're dripping wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, uh, slipped and fell into the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nothing to laugh about!\NWhat's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you don't seem hurt.\NGo change and then we'll have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! And Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Sayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you three doing together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your father just finished\Ninterrogating us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You're the Night Baron, aren't you?!" and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! That's a lovely dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But be careful. Some perverted wolf might be on the prowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:17.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That old perv just doesn't learn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} signed you up\Nfor this mystery tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Akiko's a huge fan\Nof Yusaku Kudo's novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially the Night Baron ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows more about\Nthe Night Baron than I!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even my hairstyle\Nis the same as his!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not the only expert\Non the Night Baron...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope that's food for thought.\NNow if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's{\i0} why Mom ran out on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quit ogling her, Satoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:04.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That {\i1}is{\i0} one great outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:10.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? The old perv didn't\Neven glance at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:13.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe she's not his type?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:19.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's Kaneshiro{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}, Room 2001...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Looks like Shizue Hayashi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} isn't with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:25.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Okay! Time to do some investigating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just the toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! You've had too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, mister, are you after the\Ncomputer virus too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Conan Edogawa from Room 1902.\NDo you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From whom did you hear about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The people on the tour keep\Ntalking about a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't know why\Nthey're talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All they should know is that\Nit's the "ultimate program..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was once a mysterious\Ncomputer virus that infected
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,computers at large corporations\Nand ravaged all the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, it is an unstoppable\Nand undetectable "perfect program."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, it was so elusive\Nthat the people named it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Night Baron!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Night Baron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone who knows\Ncomputers knows its name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:33.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see. And the tour organizer\Nis also named the Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:37.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that gives some idea as to\Nthe contents of the program!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hearing that name\Nbrings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of my son who\Ndied four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Son?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing! Bye, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Shizue{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.\NThat lad is one sharp rascal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:05.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's Kon'no{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} from Room 2002.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:07.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Looks like he's on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wonder what he's talking about{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it {\i1}was{\i0} Tokio Ebara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:17.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tokio Ebara? The old perv?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he was the hacker?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:26.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A hacker?! A person who\Nsteals computer data?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want one of these someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch Satomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the name of my mother\Nwho died last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Satomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:51.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whew, you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:55.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This guy's named his PC\Nafter his dead mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:59.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh? The old perv's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miss! Do you know where the person who was sitting here went?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went back to his room\Nto do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, if you know him,\Ncould you return this to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:15.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, he had this necktie wrapped around his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you "Ah, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}" me! Always sneaking around like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} all went to their rooms long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Looks like Dad's not back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah right, you flirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you've had\Ntoo much to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She says I was eyeing the waitress...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll go up to the top\Nlounge until she cools off...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:59.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come too, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just forget about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:09.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The starry sky looks so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but not nearly as pretty as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just teasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, the ocean's pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oceans sure are creepy at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Maeda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, when did you first meet Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid. I was best\Nfriends with her older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died three years ago, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s brother passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:49.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sounds like everyone else here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}. Where did the old man go anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him earlier with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamijo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from Room 2102, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:04.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Forgot about the {\i1}other{\i0} old pervert...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so you were married...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I divorced three years ago, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would anyone divorce\Nsuch a beautiful woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, could you tell me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know who the Night\NBaron is by now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you! The hotel fee's at stake here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! At least a hint!\NPlease, Mr. Great Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's got great boobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:47.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This could be one fun night!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, guess I should\Nget back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, get lost already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiko should have cooled off by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus I'd get bitten if\NI stay with you any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...by your little bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, do you know what the virus is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Virus? Like a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevermind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of weird question was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:28.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The perfect computer virus, "Night Baron".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:32.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}With it, one could threaten banks or corporations
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:34.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}out of large sums of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:38.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure lots of people would like to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:44.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But what is the tour organizer trying to do by gathering such people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:46.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is it just a game?! Or maybe—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.46,0:23:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's disturbing that the immortal Night Baron would perish...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did the Night Baron fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:23:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:24:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, this knot is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.44,0:24:08.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Night Baron!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:14.95,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.95,0:24:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-N-N-N-Next Conan's Hint: Karate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.14,0:24:21.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} plays a big part next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.86,0:24:23.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} and the old man togeth—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.01,0:24:23.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hi-yah!
